The article at the infringing location is a word by word copy from our original, copyright protected article. The copyrighted work reproduced at the allegedly infringing location is beginning with the following text:

"We all know that Windows 8 Developer Preview was released few weeks ago for use by general public. Lot of new features of Windows 8 were introduced during the Build conference where Windows 8 Developer Preview was released. But some features were also removed due to security reasons."
